ldap过滤器结构表
    Fileter = (filtercomp)
    Filtercomp = and / or / not / item
    And = & filterlist
    Or = | filterlist
    Not = ! filter
    Filterlist = 1*filter
    Item = simple / present / substring
    Simple = “=” / “~=” / ”>=” / “
